<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>make down a bed • make up a bed</xh5><p> <i>make down a bed—</i>prepare sleeping accommodation not previously available (when one has a visitor, etc.): Are you going to sleep here tonight; if you are, my wife will <u>make down a bed</u> for you.</p><p> <i>make up a bed</i>— = make down a bed: She <u>made him up a bed</u> on the high white divan in her living-room—not a heap of sleeping-bags and blankets but a real bed.</p><p> <i>See also: make a bed / make one’s bed.</i></p> </entry>
